title: Thieving/Level up table
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Thieving/Level up table
LevelNew abilities
Each level
  • Completing the Easy Ardougne Diary grants a 10% increased chance to steal from a stall in Ardougne
  • Completing the Medium Ardougne Diary grants a 10% increased chance to pickpocket in Ardougne
  • Completing the Hard Ardougne Diary grants a 10% increased chance to pickpocket in Gielinor
  • There is a better gem stall found inside Mor Ul Rek that gives better gem quality, uncut, and cut versions of the gems
  • Wearing the full rogue equipment grants double pick pocketing loot
